data.description: Come see this beautiful home with three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a bonus room on a lovely cul-de-sac! Location is perfect with easy access to Mountain Home. As you enter the home, you'll find two bedrooms and a bathroom - check out the recently installed carpet in all of the bedrooms! The bonus room is perfect for all of your dreams - home gym, playroom, office, maybe all of the above with this amount of space! The kitchen has an island, pantry, and lots of counter space. All appliances stay with this home, including the washer and dryer. The living room is open to the kitchen and dining area, with vaulted ceilings and gorgeous laminate flooring. Easy access to the backyard. Master suite includes bathroom with oval tub and large walk-in closet. Outdoors you'll find a large side yard with plenty of space for RV parking. This move-in ready home has been professionally cleaned and is ready to be where you make your next memories.
